N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 49.6 - Records and reports

State Regulations

The director of the program shall maintain such records and submit such reports, including an annual report, as may be required by the commissioner. The annual report shall include the status of all former residents who have not complied with their two-year service obligation agreement. Notes
